title: Macron visits cyclone-wrecked Mayotte as death toll expected to rise
description: Scientists at the Imperial College London say climate change likely intensified Tropical Cyclone Chido from a category three to a category four storm.
content: France's President Emmanuel Macron travelled on Thursday to the Indian Ocean archipelago of Mayotte to survey the devastation that Cyclone Chido wrought across the French territory over the weekend, … [+4428 chars]
de: Macron besucht das vom Zyklon zerstörte Mayotte, da die Zahl der Todesopfer voraussichtlich steigen wird. Wissenschaftler am Imperial College London gehen davon aus, dass der Klimawandel den tropischen Wirbelsturm Chido wahrscheinlich von der Kategorie drei auf die Kategorie vier verstärkt hat.
en: Macron visits cyclone-wrecked Mayotte as death toll expected to rise. Scientists at the Imperial College London say climate change likely intensified Tropical Cyclone Chido from a category three to a category four storm.
